---
description: Nanobox lets you focus on code rather than configuration, providing a seamless dev to production workflow.
---

%h1#home-title
  Nanobox Documentation

%p.center Nanobox takes care of the tedium and makes it easy to develop, deploy, and manage your application both locally and in production.

%a#guides-block{ href: "https://guides.nanobox.io"}
  %h5 Getting Started
  %p The Nanobox guides provide step-by-step instructions for getting started with your language or framework of choice.

#home-topics
  - data.home_links.sections.each do |s|
    %h3= s.title
    - if s.caption
      %p.caption= s.caption
    - s.topics.each do |t|
      .topic-group
        - if t.title
          %h5= t.title
        %ul
          - t.links.each do |l|
            %li= link_to l.text, l.link
          - if t.more
            %li= link_to 'More...', t.more, class: 'more'
